Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.47,0:01:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs16\pos(252.48,280.665)}-- 安迪·沃霍爾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.38,0:01:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,加州北部 1958年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.98,0:01:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你是個男人{\fs14}\NThe fifties are grand time ...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.03,0:01:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,五十年代可是段大好時光{\fs14}\N... if you are a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.12,0:01:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫迪克·諾蘭 我靠寫東西維持生計{\fs14}\NI am Dick Dolly I make things up for living.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:01:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我是個記者{\fs14}\NI'm a reporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我從業以來報道過的最離奇的故事{\fs14}\NIt's the strangest goddammit story that I've ever covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.85,0:02:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,故事從瑪格麗特·奧布裡希離開 她那令人窒息的丈夫那天開始{\fs14}\NIt start the day Margaret Olmprich walk out of her suffocated husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.09,0:02:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那時單身媽媽還遠未流行{\fs14}\Nlong before it became a fashionable thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.96,0:02:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 簡{\fs14}\NCome on, Jane.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:04:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,北灘 舊金山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,美女 你來了 你現在在北灘了{\fs14}\NSugar, you've made it, you're at North Beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧你這身打扮 德瓊{\fs14}\NLook at you, Dierdre!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我荻安{\fs14}\NDeeAnn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白 觸景生情 {\fs14}\NI know, but I came on this scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荻安就像是我媽會給我起的名字{\fs14}\N DeeAnn just sound like something my mom would call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那你還在四處尋訪嗎 安定下來沒{\fs14}\NSo, are you flipping through all this? are you settled?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 簡還好嗎 - 好 她很好{\fs14}\N- How is Jane? - Well, Jane is well
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在一所不錯的小學就讀 {\fs14}\NShe is going to this sweet little school,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也知道離了父親她也挺不容易的{\fs14}\Nyou know it's really hard without her father
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 也不知道我們能不能 - 別說了{\fs14}\N- just don't know we gonna be able to... - Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你會好起來的{\fs14}\NYou better off
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,老實說 我也從沒喜歡過弗蘭克這傢伙{\fs14}\NTo be honest, I never like Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你可是伴娘{\fs14}\NYou are a bridesmaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 所以也不好說人閒話{\fs14}\NExactly, that's why I couldn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不過如果還有下次的話 我會直言不諱的{\fs14}\NBut  if I see you run off again, I will tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,現在 跟我去玩吧{\fs14}\NNow come on, let's have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.86,0:04:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,想聽爵士樂 去"飢餓的我"夜店{\fs14}\NFor jazz, check out Hungry i.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,意大利餐館 瓦內薩餐廳{\fs14}\NFor Italian, Vanessa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.57,0:04:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,禱告的話 可以試試佛堂{\fs14}\NFor salvation, try the Buddhist Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,欣賞藝術 就去六號藝廊{\fs14}\NFor Art, Six Gallery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,今天只有現代派{\fs14}\NToday only show Modern?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都只展示現代派{\fs14}\NEveryone only shows Modern.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,在地下室 還有有意式(濃咖啡){\fs14}\NAnd in basement, they have espresso.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,意式什麼 那是啥玩意 煙嗎{\fs14}\NEspresso, What's that, is it like whiffer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:04:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要學習的還有很多呢{\fs14}\NYou have a lot to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那個年代 沒工作或發展前途{\fs14}\NBack then, women didn't live...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,女人怎麼過得下去{\fs14}\N...not without a job or prospects.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.84,0:05:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,而她全部的家當就是後備箱裡的畫{\fs14}\NAll she has is her painting in the trunk. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,和後座上的女兒{\fs14}\N...and her daughter in the back seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你好運{\fs14}\NGood luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我們這裡沒多少女職員{\fs14}\NWe don't get many ladies in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那你丈夫同意你出來工作了嗎{\fs14}\NSo your husband aproves you working?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.95,0:05:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我和我丈夫分開了{\fs14}\NMy husband and I are seperated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,分開{\fs14}\NSeperated?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白我沒有工作經驗 {\fs14}\NI realize I have no employment experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我真的很需要這份工作{\fs14}\N but I really do need this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我有個女而要撫養{\fs14}\NI have a daughter to support.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:05:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刀之類的工具我不在行 {\fs14}\NI am not very good at tool knive and hone,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.89,0:06:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我熱愛繪畫{\fs14}\N but I do like to paint.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我把畫冊拿來給你看下{\fs14}\NSo I could just show you my portfolio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.58,0:06:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我在納什維爾的沃特金斯美院上的學{\fs14}\NI studied at the Watkins Art Institute, Nashville.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,去紐約學的插畫{\fs14}\Ntook some illustration classes in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這幅是我的蠟筆作品{\fs14}\NThis is a soft pastel I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.46,0:06:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,這幅是碳筆作品{\fs14}\NThis is a charcoal portrait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白我們只是傢俱公司吧{\fs14}\NYou do understand this is a furniture company?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有沒有喜歡的 - 我喜歡這邊的{\fs14}\N- You see anything like? - I like those over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,它們真的很漂亮{\fs14}\NThey are relly neat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你的畫很可愛{\fs14}\NYour stuff is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝{\fs14}\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,多少錢{\fs14}\NHow much?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,今天特價 2美元{\fs14}\NToday's special, two dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 1美元行嗎 - 也行{\fs14}\N- I give you one. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.51,0:07:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 過去吧 - 坐那裡去{\fs14}\N- Go ahead. - Go ahead and have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什麼名字{\fs14}\NWhat's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我叫多利 - 多利{\fs14}\N- My name is Dolly. - Dolly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 幾歲了 - 今年9歲了{\fs14}\N- How old are you? - I'm 9 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.06,0:07:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,九歲了啊{\fs14}\NNine years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.85,0:07:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 像莫奈的畫 - 莫奈{\fs14}\N- Looks like Monet. - Monet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.85,0:07:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(202.2,29.121)} 克勞德·莫奈 : 法國畫家 印象派代表人物和創始人之一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.84,0:07:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太過獎了{\fs14}\NThat's hell of a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.36,0:07:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,如果容我禮貌的唱下反調 我更傳統 更像畢沙羅{\fs14}\NIf I may respectfully disagree, I'm more a traditional Pissarro
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.36,0:07:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(186,37.445)}卡米耶·畢沙羅：法國印象派畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,來 靠近瞧瞧{\fs14}\NCome, come a little closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧這大膽的構圖 生動的色彩{\fs14}\NSee these daring spacing, bold color!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,想摸摸看嗎{\fs14}\NYou wanna touch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,來嘛 來摸摸看{\fs14}\NCome on, come on, do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.47,0:08:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是吹牛哦 摸是摸不壞的{\fs14}\NI don't lay it on thick, you not gonna break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,價格35美元{\fs14}\NIt's $ 35.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你們能等我一會兒嗎{\fs14}\NWould you excuse me one second?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.34,0:08:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 畫給你 - 謝謝{\fs14}\N- Here you go. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你賺些零錢太屈才了{\fs14}\NYou're better than spare change.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你不該賣這麼便宜{\fs14}\NShouldn't sell youself so cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.68,0:08:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他們喜歡我的畫就好{\fs14}\NWell I'm just glad he like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你已經有一定水準了{\fs14}\NYou past that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你的作品洋溢著你的心血{\fs14}\Nyour heart is in your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.73,0:08:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,敢問芳名{\fs14}\NWhat's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪格麗特{\fs14}\NMargaret
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那你更願意什麼呢 和那些姑娘打情罵俏吧{\fs14}\NWhat would you rather have? flirting with those girls over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我和你一樣 瑪格麗特...{\fs14}\NNo, I, like you, Margaret ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,奧布裡希{\fs14}\N... Ulbrich.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道嗎 瑪格麗特·奧布裡希 你太低估自己了{\fs14}\NYou know, Margaret Ulbrich, you undervalue yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我教你一手{\fs14}\NLet me show you how is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,小妹妹{\fs14}\NLittle girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你想不想讓世界著名的{\fs14}\NHow would you like your portrait sketched by ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,灣區女王，瑪格麗特·奧布裡希{\fs14}\N... world renowned Margaret Ulbrich,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,給你作幅畫{\fs14}\N... queen of the bay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.72,0:09:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,分分鐘就能捕獲你的神韻{\fs14}\Nin mere minutes she capture you soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不要 - 為什麼不呢{\fs14}\N- Nah. - Why nay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,難道你不想像這被畫的漂漂亮亮的嗎{\fs14}\NDon't you wish this were you in this beautiful painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,這畫的是我{\fs14}\NThat is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那畫的也是我 ...{\fs14}\NAnd That's me ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.27,0:09:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,這幅畫開始時是我 然後媽媽把它改成了中國小男孩{\fs14}\Nthat starts is me, then mother change it into chinese boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.39,0:09:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那我道歉{\fs14}\NMy apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全誤會了{\fs14}\NI misconstrue the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.54,0:09:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最好趕在奧布裡希先生回來 {\fs14}\NI'd better mosey along before Mr. Olbrich comes back,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賞我個黑眼圈前溜走吧{\fs14}\Nsocks me in the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.42,0:09:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,奧布裡希先生和我們不是一家人了{\fs14}\NMr. Olbrich is out of the picture
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 晚上好 亨利 - 基恩先生{\fs14}\N- Good evening, Henry! - Mr. Keane!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.93,0:09:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉沒有提前通知你{\fs14}\NSorry for not calling first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.52,0:09:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我瞧瞧 你的老位置空著{\fs14}\NLet's see, your regular table is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.81,0:09:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,女士 晚上好啊 這邊請{\fs14}\NMadame, good evening,  follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不用付錢{\fs14}\NAnd I don't have to pay,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我贈送了一幅畫給廚師{\fs14}\N I'm set because I give a chef a painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.39,0:10:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你知道他怎麼說嗎 - 什麼{\fs14}\N- You know what he said? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他說 "沒人能像沃爾特·基恩那樣把蒙馬特畫的這麼美"{\fs14}\NHe said, "no one paints Montmartre like Walter Keane!"
