Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,真羨慕你在巴黎呆過{\fs14}\NI can't believe you lived in Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我人生中最美的一段時光{\fs14}\NBest time of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我至今連飛機都沒坐過{\fs14}\NI never even on a airplane.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你得去親身體驗生活{\fs14}\NYou have to experience these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你得抓住機會{\fs14}\NYou have to grab on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我想當藝術家，說走就走{\fs14}\NI want to be a artist, I just went.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,0:10:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,去了法蘭西藝術院學繪畫{\fs14}\NStudied painting at the Beaux Arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,住在左岸的畫室裡 終日與紅酒 麵包為伴{\fs14}\NLive in the left bank studio, survive on bread and wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194.4,34.948)}位於巴黎塞納河左岸,是作家,學者和藝術家的彙集之所
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你是浪漫型的{\fs14}\NYou are a romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你說的太對了{\fs14}\NDamn right you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.77,0:10:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,當然 拋下富足的生活並不容易{\fs14}\NOf course, walking away from bourgeois things wasn't easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我得辭掉工作{\fs14}\NI have to quit my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,離開妻子{\fs14}\NLeave my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.54,0:10:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,做這些抉擇並不容易{\fs14}\NYeah, these choices aren't easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我的人生從不自由{\fs14}\NI never act freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,為人女 為人妻...{\fs14}\NI was a daughter, then wife ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.19,0:11:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,然後為人母{\fs14}\N... then a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我所有的畫都是簡 因為她就是我的全部{\fs14}\NAll of my paintings are Jane, because she is all I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.07,0:11:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,別看低自己的作品{\fs14}\NDon't knock off you work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你天賦過人{\fs14}\NYou have amazing talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你能打量一個人 然後把他畫出來{\fs14}\NYou can look someone, capture them on canvas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你能畫人物{\fs14}\NYou can paint people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.75,0:11:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我只能畫風景{\fs14}\NI can only paint things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.40,0:11:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,恩 我的街景畫{\fs14}\NYeah, my street things are ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.65,0:11:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是挺迷人的{\fs14}\N... charming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.43,0:11:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,可是到最後 它們只是一堆樓閣 街道的{\fs14}\NBut, at the end of day, they are just collections of ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,大合集{\fs14}\N... buildings and sidewalks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,沃爾特 我打賭你什麼都能畫{\fs14}\NWalter, I bet you can paint anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,當你用那樣的眼神看我 我會狠狠的墜入愛河{\fs14}\NWhen you look at me like that, I could fall a lot hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉我失態了{\fs14}\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我們之間發展得太快了{\fs14}\NThis just moving really fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:11:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我很久都沒約過會了{\fs14}\NI haven't been on a date in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,簡 你彆扭扭捏捏的{\fs14}\NJane, sweetie, stop wiggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽 這麼些年下來你應該對我的臉再熟悉不過了吧{\fs14}\NMother, after all these time you must know what my face looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你的畫布還空著{\fs14}\NHey, you canvas is blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.10,0:12:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,靈感是強求不來的{\fs14}\NYou can't rush for inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,別煩基恩叔叔 你也知道才思泉湧 由內而外{\fs14}\NDon't bother Mr. Keane, you know creativity come from within.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,別擔心 她一點都不煩人{\fs14}\NDon't worry, she is not bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,能問你個問題嗎{\fs14}\NCan I ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.14,0:12:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這大的嚇人的眼睛有什麼寓意嗎{\fs14}\NWhat's that with big crazy eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你能從中看到什麼{\fs14}\NI believe you can see things in the eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛是通往心靈的窗戶{\fs14}\NEye is the window to the soul
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 不過你畫的兩個餅{\fs14}\NYeah, but you paint two pancakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.98,0:13:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,比例誇張{\fs14}\NWay out of proportion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛是我表達自己情感的方式{\fs14}\NEyes are how I express my emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.31,0:13:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我總是把它們畫成這樣{\fs14}\NI always draw them like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我小的時候動過手術 結果失聰了一段時間{\fs14}\NWhen I was little, I had surgery left me deaf for a period.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.45,0:13:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,聽不見聲音 於是我總是乾瞪著眼{\fs14}\NI couldn't hear, so I found myself staring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,看著別人的眼睛{\fs14}\NAnd idle on peoples' eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.62,0:13:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,沃爾特{\fs14}\NWalter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.08,0:13:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 我就覺得是你{\fs14}\NHey, I thought that was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.27,0:13:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,很高興見到你{\fs14}\NI am gald to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.22,0:13:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 那個問題你有消息了嗎{\fs14}\NHey, any heard back from the city on that setback?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.23,0:13:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我的人很需要那個樓層銷售的方案{\fs14}\NMy guy really need versions for the forth floor retail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.98,0:13:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,週四就會曉得了 {\fs14}\NWe will hear from permits by Thursday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 那太好了 我去告訴設計師{\fs14}\NYeah, that's terrific, I'll tell the architect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼情況{\fs14}\NWhat was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒想讓你知道的{\fs14}\NI didn't want you to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我從事房地產生意{\fs14}\NI'm in comercial real estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:13:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,房地產經紀人{\fs14}\NYou're a realtor?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,恩 事業很成功 收入傲人 市區辦公{\fs14}\NYeah, hugely successful realtor, top earner, downtomn office.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,有三年多了{\fs14}\NThree years running.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.71,0:14:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你還難以啟齒{\fs14}\NAnd you are ashame?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,傻子都可以幹這一行{\fs14}\NAny blockhead can arrange a sublease.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直想的是{\fs14}\NAll I ever wanted ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,成為一名靠自己手藝謀生的藝術家{\fs14}\N... is to surpport myself as a artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,嘗試過後卻沒成功{\fs14}\NTry to make a clear break, couldn't cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.52,0:14:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我只能做週日畫家{\fs14}\NI am just a sunday painter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.64,0:14:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝，進來這裡吧{\fs14}\NThank you, just come right in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.83,0:14:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,就放在那吧{\fs14}\NJust set it down over here ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這兒 {\fs14}\NRight here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩 就那 那樣不會擋道{\fs14}\NYeah, that's great, I just like to keep it out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我還在畫的一幅作品{\fs14}\NThis is one of them I'm working on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,還在想著怎麼畫好{\fs14}\NYou can see I'm working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我收了信{\fs14}\NI got the mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.79,0:15:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,出什麼事了{\fs14}\NWhat's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.02,0:15:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,弗蘭克想把簡從我身邊奪走{\fs14}\NFrank wants take Jane away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.95,0:15:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他說我是個不稱職的母親 - 你是個完美的母親{\fs14}\N- He say I'm a unfitted mother ... - You're a perfect mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.67,0:16:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他跟法庭說簡需要個完整的家庭{\fs14}\NHe told the court that she lacks a proper home ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,而我這個單身母親是沒法給她提供的{\fs14}\N... it is beyond my capability as a single mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.97,0:16:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嫁給我{\fs14}\NMarry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別找借口說不 {\fs14}\NDon't think of a reason to say no,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.65,0:16:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可有無數的理由說服你{\fs14}\NI got a million reasons to say yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.76,0:16:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我知道這有點不合常理 - 是有點{\fs14}\N- I know it makes no sense. - no, it doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,只是想想我們會多開心{\fs14}\NJust think the fun we'll have.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.70,0:16:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我會好好愛護你們母女倆{\fs14}\NI'm gonna to take care of you girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪格利特 我向你求婚 你答不答應{\fs14}\NMargaret, I'm on my knee, come on what do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們結婚吧{\fs14}\Nlet's get married!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我們週末就可以在夏威夷了{\fs14}\NWe could be at Hawaii by the weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,夏威夷 結婚{\fs14}\NHawaii, marriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:50.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道 沃爾特 {\fs14}\NI don't know, Walter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜歡你 只是現在我有點不知所措{\fs14}\NI'm crazy about you, I'm just really overwhelmed righ now ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.39,0:16:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼我們要去夏威夷{\fs14}\N... why we go to Hawaii, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.04,0:16:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你是個公主 {\fs14}\NBecause you're a pricess,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就該在天堂下結婚{\fs14}\Nyou deserve to get married in paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.44,0:17:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你說的沒錯 這真是人間天堂{\fs14}\NYou were right, it's paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.34,0:17:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,這色彩只能是上帝的手筆{\fs14}\NOnly God could creat these colours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.43,0:17:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道你會喜歡{\fs14}\NI knew I'd love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我們可以永遠待在這嗎{\fs14}\NCan we just stay here forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.37,0:17:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠我不敢說 {\fs14}\NI don't know about forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.89,0:17:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過多待一星期是我想是可以安排的{\fs14}\Nbut I guess I could arrange for another week.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那是瀑布 空氣超清新 你可以嘗嘗{\fs14}\NThat's waterfall, and air is so fresh, you can taste it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是個古老的神壇{\fs14}\NThis is an ancient altar,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.19,0:18:25.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是凱恩的雕像 他是創造之神{\fs14}\Nthat's a statue of Kane, the God of Creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.11,0:18:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我對他許了個願{\fs14}\NI said a prayer to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.97,0:18:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是沃爾特和簡 {\fs14}\NThat's Walter and Jane,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有他們一起堆的沙堡{\fs14}\N they build that sand castle together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.22,0:18:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一切都發生得太快了吧 {\fs14}\NWell, these just all happening mighty quick,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.68,0:18:36.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛搬過來{\fs14}\N by the time you moved here ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我們分開沒兩天，你就已經嫁人了{\fs14}\N... I had two days, you're already married.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想是因為我的人生空了一塊 {\fs14}\NWell, I thought there is a void in my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃爾特正好填上{\fs14}\Nand Walter fills it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.73,0:18:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃爾特填的真是時候 {\fs14}\NWalter fills a lot of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.48,0:18:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁虛而入{\fs14}\N he did every skirt in the acts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你說的可是我老公啊{\fs14}\NThat's my husband you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.85,0:18:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 所以我才實話實說{\fs14}\NI know, that's why I brought it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.37,0:18:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是天真{\fs14}\NI'm not naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧我是天真了點 不過我可沒胡亂嫁人{\fs14}\NI am naive, but I know who I married.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.00,0:19:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃爾特這事是急了點 {\fs14}\NWalter can be rush,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過他經濟條件好 {\fs14}\Nbut he is a good provider,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.69,0:19:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且對簡視如己出{\fs14}\Nand he is really wonderful with Jane.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.17,0:19:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只是想重新開始 {\fs14}\NWe just looking to make a fresh start,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.43,0:19:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一單身母親帶著閨女得現實點{\fs14}\N I'm a divorcer with a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有沃爾特是我的福氣{\fs14}\NWalter is a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.66,0:19:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"你正邁向未知的成功之旅"{\fs14}\N"You are on a threshold of untold success."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,它的高明之處在於構圖的自發性{\fs14}\NIts brilliant is about the compostion of spontaneity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.03,0:19:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,圖像本身沒有一個視覺吸引點{\fs14}\NThe image has no visual center for attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姿態感很強{\fs14}\N{\pos(193.2,283.827)}- It's quite gestural.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:40.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到點子上了 很明顯信奉塔希主義{\fs14}\N{\pos(193.2,283.827)}- Oh definitively, strongly influenced by Tachism.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(196.8,34.948)}奉塔希主義：滴色派,抽像派繪畫法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.27,0:19:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽說泰布·亨特來這裡時對某幅畫表現過興趣{\fs14}\NI heard Tab Hunter was in here looking at one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.27,0:19:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(192,30.786)}泰布·亨特: 演員 歌手 作家
