Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.09,0:29:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你出名了{\fs14}\NYou were a hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.90,0:29:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚賺翻了{\fs14}\NWhat a night.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.56,0:29:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我賣光了你的<大眼睛>{\fs14}\NI sold out all your .
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.31,0:29:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,200塊{\fs14}\N$ 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.68,0:29:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他們可喜歡你的畫了{\fs14}\NThey adore you!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.27,0:29:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,因為那篇報道 夜店人滿為患{\fs14}\NBecause of that article, the joint was packed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.27,0:29:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了很多著名記者 畫作一搶而空{\fs14}\NThere are famous journalists, sold all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.15,0:29:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要更多的畫{\fs14}\N I need more paintings!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.33,0:29:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...{\fs14}\N...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.97,0:30:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這是個大好機會 我們會組成完美團隊{\fs14}\NThis is a opportunity, we gonna make a cracker jack team!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.51,0:30:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我駐紮夜店推廣 你在家傾情創作{\fs14}\NMe show them in the club, you got here doing what you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.42,0:30:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,快拿開{\fs14}\NGet out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.17,0:30:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我愛你{\fs14}\NI love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.92,0:31:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這些眼睛真攝魂{\fs14}\NThe eyes are so powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.64,0:31:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,知道嗎 有位詩人曾經說到 ...{\fs14}\NYou know a poet once said ...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.67,0:31:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛是通向心靈的窗戶{\fs14}\N... The eyes are the windows of the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.99,0:31:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才把它們畫這麼大 這是我的一貫作風{\fs14}\NThat's why I paint them so big, I always done it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.96,0:31:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你對這種畫風感興趣 我最新的一幅作品{\fs14}\NIf you're interested in that style, one of new pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.61,0:31:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,畫的是一個身著黃衣的金髮小姑娘{\fs14}\NI have a little blond girl in a yellow dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.89,0:31:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,會讓你心都碎了{\fs14}\NIt'll tear you heart out.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.84,0:31:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,寶貝 你來這做什麼{\fs14}\NBaby, what're you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.55,0:31:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼要撒謊{\fs14}\NWhy are you lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.83,0:32:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉失陪一會兒{\fs14}\NExcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.12,0:32:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,讚賞的是我的作品 你幹嘛冒名頂替{\fs14}\NYou are taking credit for something that isn't yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.36,0:32:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想做成生意{\fs14}\NI'm just trying close a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.61,0:32:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這些孩子是我生命的一部分{\fs14}\NThese children are part of my being.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.84,0:32:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是為了賣畫 你也知道能和畫家面對面的話 {\fs14}\NI must say, you know buyers would pay more
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.17,0:32:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,買家會願意下血本{\fs14}\Nif they meet the painter.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.05,0:32:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他們見不到我是因為你讓我待在家裡{\fs14}\NThey couldn't meet me because you told me to stay home.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.33,0:32:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜點 只要能賺錢{\fs14}\NLook, we're making money.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.91,0:32:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你賺的 我賺的 有分別嗎？{\fs14}\NYour pocket, my pocket, where is the difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.39,0:32:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本不把這當回事{\fs14}\NYou're taking this so lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.87,0:32:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,哪有 我不是想拔高自己{\fs14}\NNot at all, this is not about ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.88,0:32:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你如果想說街景是你畫的 我沒意見{\fs14}\NYou want to say you did the street scene, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.45,0:32:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,說是猴子畫的我也不在乎{\fs14}\NI don't care,say a monkey painted them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.82,0:32:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊 {\fs14}\NOh God,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.47,0:32:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以不加思索就說出這些話來{\fs14}\Nyou could just dash your word without any emotional connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.19,0:32:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,寶貝 我只是想讓全世界都看到我們的畫{\fs14}\NHoney, I just wanna share it with the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.31,0:32:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你想讓自己的孩子蝸居過苦日子{\fs14}\NWould you rather your children pouting in closet ...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.17,0:32:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,還是住大房子衣食無憂{\fs14}\N... or hanging in someone's living room
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.87,0:32:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這人什麼來頭{\fs14}\NWho is that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.11,0:32:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那是迪諾·奧利維蒂{\fs14}\NThat is Dino Olivetti.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.61,0:32:58.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃爾特 別想高攀{\fs14}\NDon't even think about, Walter,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.39,0:32:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不會說英語{\fs14}\N he doeson't speak  lack of english.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.84,0:33:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧利維蒂先生被這幅畫迷住了 {\fs14}\NMr Olivetti is enchanted by the painting,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.33,0:33:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想見識一下畫家本人{\fs14}\N he would like to know who is the artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.23,0:33:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,在下就是{\fs14}\NI am.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.83,0:34:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,五打五千{\fs14}\NFive grands!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.30,0:34:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我們賺了5000啊{\fs14}\NWe made  5000 dollors!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.71,0:34:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,還不是你的佳作就買了5000{\fs14}\NThat was not even for one of your good ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.30,0:34:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你指的是你的佳作吧{\fs14}\NDon't you mean your good one?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.98,0:34:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不是{\fs14}\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.17,0:34:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的 是我們的佳作之一{\fs14}\NOur, one of our good ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.53,0:34:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的畫現在被意大利企業家迪諾·奧利維蒂收藏了{\fs14}\NWe now hanging in the collection of italian industrialist Dino Olivetti.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.23,0:34:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他買我們的畫就等於一種認可{\fs14}\NWith his patronize comes credibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.88,0:34:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,有了這種認可 名望隨之而來{\fs14}\NWith credibility, comes respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.96,0:34:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那實情呢{\fs14}\NWhat about honesty?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.83,0:34:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的畫都簽的是基恩{\fs14}\NAll our paintings say Keane.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.96,0:34:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我是基恩 你也是基恩{\fs14}\NI'm Keane, you're Keane.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.01,0:35:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,從今往後 我們不分彼此{\fs14}\NFrom now on, we're one of the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.02,0:35:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,有人向我爆料說市長今天預期會收到個大驚喜{\fs14}\NMy source tell me the mayor expect big surprise today. </ I>
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.05,0:35:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,代表全世界的兒童 我把這幅畫贈與{\fs14}\NOn behalf of the children of the world, I pesent this painting ...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.49,0:35:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,舊金山市長{\fs14}\N... to the mayor of San Francisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.28,0:35:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,外面有人通知我蘇聯大使正在來訪{\fs14}\NMy man on the street tells me Soviet ambassador in town as speak. </ I>
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.05,0:35:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,以文化傳遞和平{\fs14}\NIn the interest of peace throught culture ...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.15,0:35:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我把這幅畫贈與蘇聯人民{\fs14}\N... I donate this painting to the people of Soviet Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.22,0:35:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上9點半 瓊·克勞福德在紫洋蔥預訂了位子{\fs14}\NThe Purple Onion, 21:30, Joan Crawford have dinner reservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.97,0:35:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,克勞福德女士 為了向你的表演致敬{\fs14}\NMrs. Crawford, in recognition of your cinematic craft ...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.56,0:35:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我們贈送這幅肖像畫給你{\fs14}\N... we bestow with this painting of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.07,0:35:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,這秘密不新鮮了{\fs14}\NThe cat is out of the bag. </ I>
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.21,0:36:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我們本地的名人沃爾特·基恩的個人畫廊即將開館{\fs14}\NI can revail our local luminary Walter Kean is open his own gallery. </ I>
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.96,0:36:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,魯本看到這還不得氣死{\fs14}\NRuben gonna choke when he see these.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.49,0:36:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我記得是我媽畫的{\fs14}\NI remember my mom painted that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.01,0:36:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你確信？那可是好久以前的事了{\fs14}\NAre you sure? that would been awhile ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.58,0:36:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我記得很清楚{\fs14}\NSure it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.26,0:36:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是在過去公寓的廚房裡畫的我{\fs14}\NIt was at old apartment you had me sit still in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.78,0:36:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不對 乖乖 你搞錯了 這是我畫的{\fs14}\NNo, sweetie, you're comfused. I painted that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.35,0:36:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 是我媽畫的 我穿的那件羊毛衫{\fs14}\NNo, mother did, I wear my wool dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.72,0:36:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,很多小女生都穿那種衣服{\fs14}\NLots of girls have that dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.69,0:36:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你眼力不錯{\fs14}\NYou have a good eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.93,0:36:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,其實我是照你媽媽的風格畫的{\fs14}\NI painted it, and try to mimic your mom's style
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.09,0:36:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你記得嗎 你媽過去的繪畫風格{\fs14}\NYou know, the style she used to paint.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.76,0:36:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那你真是學得很像{\fs14}\NYou did a really good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.78,0:37:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你好{\fs14}\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.44,0:37:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我從沒做過這個{\fs14}\NI'm sorry, I've never done this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.83,0:37:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我從小就接受的是衛理公會 如果這不允許我就走{\fs14}\NI was raised Methodist, so if that's a problem I could go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.26,0:37:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不會 請坐吧 我們不會趕人走的{\fs14}\NNo no, please, we don't chase people away.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.21,0:37:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,何事困擾著你{\fs14}\NWhat is troubling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.50,0:37:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我對自己的孩子撒謊{\fs14}\NI lie to my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.98,0:37:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼那樣做{\fs14}\NWhy did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.85,0:37:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我丈夫唆使我去幹的{\fs14}\NMy husband he pressure me to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.21,0:37:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我從沒對她撒過謊 我不是那種人{\fs14}\NI just never lie to her, I am not that kind of person.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.37,0:37:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那你丈夫是嗎{\fs14}\NIs your husban that kind of person?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.72,0:37:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我不那樣看他{\fs14}\NI don't think him that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.78,0:37:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他喜歡講講故事 吹吹牛什麼的{\fs14}\NHe likes to tell stories, and he exaggerates about.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.77,0:37:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他本質不壞{\fs14}\NHe is a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.69,0:38:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是想攢夠錢好買我們自己的房子{\fs14}\NHe just try to save enough money to buy a house for the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.99,0:38:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子呢 這謊言會給她帶來傷害嗎{\fs14}\NBut what about the chlid, will this lie bring harm to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.35,0:38:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,傷害  不 不會{\fs14}\NHarm? no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.22,0:38:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是找人開解下我{\fs14}\NI'm just looking for some answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.27,0:38:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼說吧 現代社會錯綜複雜{\fs14}\NWell, the modern world is a complex place.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.30,0:38:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,有時候 不說真相的目的是為了保護孩子{\fs14}\NOccasionally, children may need to be sheltered from certain truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.30,0:38:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 不是的{\fs14}\NNo, it's not like ...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.13,0:38:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,聽起來你丈夫只想盡力改善{\fs14}\NIt sounds if your husband is to try to make the best of ...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.73,0:38:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,家人的處境罷了{\fs14}\N... a imperfect situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.90,0:38:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你從小接觸基督教義 知道主教導我們{\fs14}\NYou were raised Christian, you know we were taught ...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.05,0:38:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,男人是一家之主{\fs14}\N... man is the head of a household.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.96,0:38:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,或許你該相信他的判斷{\fs14}\NPerhaps  you should trust his judgement.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.11,0:38:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,基恩畫廊 開館之夜 1960年{\fs14}\NKeane Gallery, Opening Night, 1960
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.70,0:38:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得這畫現代了點 業餘了點 還有點嚇人{\fs14}\NI think it's creepy, modern, and amateurish.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.52,0:38:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,一語中的{\fs14}\NExactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.84,0:38:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我就喜歡這種畫{\fs14}\NI love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.20,0:39:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我們3個早就到了{\fs14}\NWe got here early, we are three.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.71,0:39:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝{\fs14}\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.28,0:39:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 寶貝 很棒的聚會 夢想成真了{\fs14}\NHey, baby! killer party, it's happening
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.98,0:39:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你的畫在哪{\fs14}\NSo, where is your stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.10,0:39:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我們決定做沃爾特的個人展{\fs14}\NWe decided this just be Walter show.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.76,0:39:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎 他為什麼要這樣{\fs14}\NWell, he did? why would he do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.74,0:39:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,恩 因為沃爾特比較成熟老練{\fs14}\NOh, because Walter is more established.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.23,0:39:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,有點怪啊 我真不覺得沃爾特會是去畫{\fs14}\NStrange you know, Walter doesn't really strike me ...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.94,0:39:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,楚楚可憐孤兒的類型{\fs14}\N... as cute hungry kids type.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.65,0:39:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,見到你很高興{\fs14}\NIt's really good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.11,0:39:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,感謝前來捧場{\fs14}\NThank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.39,0:39:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你丈夫真有才華{\fs14}\NYour husband's quite a talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.26,0:39:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你也作畫嗎{\fs14}\NDo you paint too?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.58,0:40:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道{\fs14}\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.86,0:40:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我對你的技巧很感興趣{\fs14}\NI'm curious about your technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.23,0:40:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,畫好那幅畫要多長時間{\fs14}\NHow long that piece take to excute?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.20,0:40:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,一個月左右吧{\fs14}\NProbably a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.76,0:40:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,先是構思 然後繪草圖 剩下嘛就是我和油畫顏料的親密時刻了{\fs14}\NFirst, thinking, sketching, then the time just me and oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.29,0:40:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,油畫顏料 那不是用的丙烯顏料嗎{\fs14}\NOil? but is it acrylics?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.25,0:40:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 那幅啊{\fs14}\NThat? yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.52,0:40:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我的腦子裡總是有各種點子鑽來鑽去(難免說錯話){\fs14}\NIt's just like a jumbo ideas rattling aroung in my brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.39,0:40:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那你的點子都是從哪來的{\fs14}\NSo where did you get your ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.81,0:40:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你的意思是{\fs14}\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.48,0:40:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我想知道為什麼畫的都是小孩子{\fs14}\NI mean why are they all images of the children?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.41,0:40:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,羅傑斯女士 我要提醒你 你可是宣過誓的{\fs14}\NMay I remind you, Mrs. Rogers,  you sworn under the oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.00,0:41:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,羅傑斯女士 你的證詞說{\fs14}\NMrs Rogers, you testify that ...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.40,0:41:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當你見到傑森·貝利·克勞利時{\fs14}\NWhen you met Jason Bailey Crowley,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.36,0:41:05.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他正和酒吧裡的一個人交談{\fs14}\N he's been talking to a man at the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.19,0:41:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你想說明什麼？{\fs14}\NI don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.49,0:41:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會只是個陌生人{\fs14}\NCouldn't it be just some stranger
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.11,0:41:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛好和貝利先生談上了呢？{\fs14}\Nwho just struck a conversation with Mr. bailey?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.89,0:41:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不是的 - 謝謝 羅傑斯女士 我的問題問完了{\fs14}\N- No! - Thank you, Mrs. Roger, that would be all.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.64,0:41:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,稍後請繼續收看 " 佩裡·梅森 "{\fs14}\NPerry Mason  will return after this. </ I>
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.85,0:41:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,紐約時報藝術評論家約翰·卡納迪{\fs14}\NNew York Times art critic John Canaday ... </ i>
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.50,0:41:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,以專業眼光剖析沃爾特·基恩的創作{\fs14}\N... with a perspective into the work of Walter Keane </ I>
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.56,0:41:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,基恩的作品完全模板化{\fs14}\NKeane's work is completely without distinction. </ I>
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.62,0:41:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,西方藝術界裡根本沒有他的一席之地{\fs14}\NHe is not a member of society western artists. </ I>
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.46,0:41:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他從未獲得任何獎項{\fs14}\NHe's won no awards. </ I>
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.48,0:41:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅僅是上過某報紙的八卦板塊{\fs14}\NHe's only known to others for his appearence
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.86,0:41:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才為人所知{\fs14}\Nin certain newspaper's gossip columns. </ I>
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.48,0:41:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,基恩先生正是為何社會大眾需要評論家 ... </ I>{\fs14}\NMr. Keane is why society need critics. </ I>
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.66,0:41:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,來保護他們不受藝術糟粕的荼毒 </ I>{\fs14}\Nto protect them from such atrocities. </ I>
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.77,0:41:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,媽{\fs14}\NMom!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.95,0:41:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,媽 我可以進來嗎{\fs14}\NMom, can I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.13,0:41:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不 別進來 我現在正忙{\fs14}\NNo, you can't, mom is busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.41,0:42:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你在幹嘛啊{\fs14}\NWhat're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.24,0:42:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,簡 乖乖 過來{\fs14}\NJane, sweetie, come.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.52,0:42:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你得尊重你媽的個人空間{\fs14}\NYou need to respect your mother's privacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.75,0:42:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,有時大人不希望被打擾{\fs14}\NSometimes grown-up need their own time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.09,0:42:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是賣冰淇淋的嗎{\fs14}\NIs that the  icecream truck?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.46,0:42:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,去給自己買個吧{\fs14}\NGo get youself a ...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.64,0:42:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,世間少有啊{\fs14}\NOut of this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.38,0:42:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道{\fs14}\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.33,0:42:51.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一切讓我有些不自在{\fs14}\NI'm not comfortable with this,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.43,0:42:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和簡過去親密無間 可現在 ...{\fs14}\NJane and I were really close, now ...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.71,0:42:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,簡很好{\fs14}\NJane is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.26,0:42:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有冰淇淋吃{\fs14}\NShe is eating icecream,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.21,0:43:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過還得指望我們給她搞定大學學費啊{\fs14}\Nshe hasn't assume she even has a college fund.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.35,0:43:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,或許我被這揮之不去的松脂味{\fs14}\NMaybe I'm just light-headed from all this turpentine ...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.75,0:43:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,熏得有點心煩意亂{\fs14}\N... up here all day
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.81,0:43:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你得幫幫我{\fs14}\NI need you help.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.41,0:43:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我想上電視去為我們的藝術辯護{\fs14}\NI want to go on television to defend our art.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.78,0:43:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 你要上電視去{\fs14}\NWait, you going on the television?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.90,0:43:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,恩 不過我該說些什麼{\fs14}\NYeah, but what am I gonna say?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.30,0:43:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,重點是什麼驅使我去創作這些畫{\fs14}\NMeaning what compells me to painted these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.40,0:43:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,或許你病態的迷戀上了小女孩{\fs14}\NMaybe you have a unhealthy obession with little girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.97,0:43:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好點子 - 對不起{\fs14}\N- Cute. - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.47,0:43:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,看上去你把自己逼上了絕路{\fs14}\NLooks like "you pin youself into a corner"
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.65,0:43:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 你想冬天有暖氣的話 就給我想想辦法{\fs14}\NYeah, you want heat this winter, help me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.05,0:43:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,沃爾特 藝術是個人的表達{\fs14}\NWalter, art is personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.89,0:43:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是什麼驅使一個成年人去畫這樣的畫{\fs14}\NWhat compells a grown man to paint a picture like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.31,0:43:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我從小與六姐妹一同成長{\fs14}\NBecause I grew up surrounded by six sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.18,0:43:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我成長在孤兒院{\fs14}\NI grew up in a orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.65,0:44:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我生活在一個大人銷聲匿跡{\fs14}\NI lived at a world where adult had vanished ...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.99,0:44:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,由小孩和小貓主宰的荒蕪大地{\fs14}\N... and kids and kittens run wild over desolate landscape?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.07,0:44:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那你的街景畫呢 你為什麼選擇畫它們{\fs14}\NWhat about your street scenes? why did you paint these?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.71,0:44:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我活在其中 親身經歷過{\fs14}\NWell I lived it, I experienced it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.09,0:44:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,走到哪都是點綴著陽光和花店的街道{\fs14}\NWas it all sunlight dappled streets and flower venders?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.03,0:44:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,當然不是{\fs14}\NOf course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.26,0:44:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那可是戰後{\fs14}\NIt was after war.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.40,0:44:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,到處都是殘垣斷壁{\fs14}\NThere was destruction everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.71,0:44:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我走遍大陸 破壞令人髮指{\fs14}\NI traveled continent, the ravages were horrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.13,0:44:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,給我藝術學生的心靈留下了創傷{\fs14}\NMy psyche was scarred in my art student days.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.25,0:44:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有什麼能像孩子的影像一樣{\fs14}\NNothing in my life has ever made such a impact
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.07,0:44:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我人生帶來如此大的衝擊{\fs14}\Nas the sight of children.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.90,0:44:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那些被戰火奪去父母和家園的無辜孩子{\fs14}\NThe war racked innocents without parents, without home.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.25,0:44:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,爭相搶奪垃圾{\fs14}\NFighting over garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.52,0:45:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是我畫家生涯開始的起點{\fs14}\NThat's when my life as a painter began at earliest.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.26,0:45:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,從那時起 我就開始創作各種大眼睛的孤兒{\fs14}\NFrom then on, I painted lost children with big eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.87,0:45:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這些大眼睛會讓人刻骨銘心 永生難忘{\fs14}\NThose eyes forever will retain their haunting quality
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.61,0:45:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,今天賣了多少{\fs14}\NHow many sales today?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.46,0:46:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就這群人 會賣得出去{\fs14}\NSales? none with this crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.13,0:46:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些都是湊熱鬧的窮鬼 {\fs14}\NThose people all lowly looks,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.84,0:46:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可買不起這裡的畫{\fs14}\N they can't afford these paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.74,0:46:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不過海報倒是發出去不少{\fs14}\NBut we have been giving away a lot of posters.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.92,0:46:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我幹過最瘋狂的事{\fs14}\NCraziest thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.93,0:46:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我開始賣海報{\fs14}\NI started charging for the posters.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.05,0:46:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,一開始5分 然後1毛 恩 這點子絕了{\fs14}\NFirst a nickel, then a dime, yes, it's cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.52,0:46:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 我又再想了想 {\fs14}\NBut, then it got me thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.30,0:46:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是願意賣一張500美元的畫{\fs14}\N would you rather sell one $ 500 painting ...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.02,0:46:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,還是一百萬張便宜的印刷海報{\fs14}\N... or millions cheaply reproduced posters?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.16,0:46:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 人們不在乎它是不是印刷的{\fs14}\NSee, folks don't care it's a copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.16,0:46:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,只要能表示他們懂點藝術{\fs14}\NThey just want art that touches them.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.90,0:46:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,然後我們可以四處開花{\fs14}\NThen we could sell it to anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.49,0:46:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,賣到世界上的任一個角落{\fs14}\NEeverywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.36,0:47:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾以為可以信任你 {\fs14}\N I used to think I could trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.36,0:47:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(196.2,54.092)}拉娜·德雷的同名主題曲 {\fs14}\NLana Del Rey - Big Eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.06,0:47:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我是你的女人{\fs14}\NI was your woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.85,0:47:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我的騎士{\fs14}\NYou were my knight
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.65,0:47:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,光彩照人的伴侶{\fs14}\Nshining companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.84,0:48:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,可沒想到 給我的愛送終的{\fs14}\NTo my surprise, my loves demise.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.93,0:48:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是他的貪婪和花言巧語{\fs14}\NWas his own greed and lullaby.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.03,0:48:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,用你的大眼睛 和你的彌天大謊{\fs14}\NWith your big eyes, and your big lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.02,0:48:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,用你的大眼睛 和你的彌天大謊{\fs14}\NWith your big eyes, and your big lies ...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.70,0:48:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,味挺大的 你該打開窗戶透透氣{\fs14}\NStinks here, you should open a window.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.58,0:48:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,現在幾點了{\fs14}\NWhat time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.98,0:48:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,六點半{\fs14}\N6:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.10,0:48:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你那畫的是什麼 讓我瞧瞧{\fs14}\NWhat you got back there? let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.51,0:48:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,沃爾特 這是給我自己畫的{\fs14}\NWalter, it's personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.03,0:48:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己的 我們是夫妻 {\fs14}\NPersonal, we married!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.02,0:48:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不該對對方有所隱瞞{\fs14}\Nwe're not suppose to have secret from each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.99,0:48:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快拿出來{\fs14}\NPut it out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.84,0:48:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這完全是另一種風格{\fs14}\NIt's completely diferent style.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.87,0:49:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,的確是啊{\fs14}\NYes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.83,0:49:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,有點像你{\fs14}\NKind of looks like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.14,0:49:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,恩 是自畫像{\fs14}\NWell, it's a self portrait.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.59,0:49:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這個我該如何解釋{\fs14}\NHow am I gonna explain that?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.60,0:49:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我在考慮{\fs14}\NI was thinking that ...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.33,0:49:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,或許簽我自己的名字{\fs14}\N... maybe I could sigh it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.28,0:49:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那聽上去讓人分不清楚啊 不是嗎{\fs14}\NThat sounds a bit comfusing? doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.41,0:49:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,'基恩'指的是我{\fs14}\NKeane means me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.56,0:49:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白 可當有人問我是否也作畫{\fs14}\NI know, but when people asks me if I paint ...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.33,0:49:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知該如何應答{\fs14}\N... I don't know how to answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.67,0:49:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,如果能挺起胸膛說那是我畫的 不是很好嗎{\fs14}\NIt would be nice to have a pride being able to say that's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.29,0:49:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟誰說了" 大眼睛 " 的事{\fs14}\NWho you tells about "Big Eyes"?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.22,0:49:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,誰也沒說{\fs14}\NNobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.37,0:49:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你跟任何人講半個字{\fs14}\NIf you tell anyone ...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.32,0:49:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的努力就全白費了{\fs14}\N... this empire collapses!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.96,0:49:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你想把錢都退回去{\fs14}\NYou wanna give back the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.38,0:49:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我們會成為詐騙犯 - 我明白{\fs14}\N- We could become Fraud! - I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.34,0:49:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,老天啊 我明白 我無時無刻不在提醒自己{\fs14}\NMy God, I know, I live with this every minute of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.71,0:49:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我保守我的諾言 從未告訴任何人{\fs14}\NI hold my end of the bargain, I have not told anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.84,0:50:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 這個就交給我來應付{\fs14}\NPlease, just let me handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.42,0:50:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪格麗特 我沒想到你也作畫{\fs14}\NI don't know you painted, Margeret.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.46,0:50:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,恩 大家都蒙在鼓裡{\fs14}\NYeah, we don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.15,0:50:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,很不幸 沒人會買女人的藝術品{\fs14}\NSadly, people don't buy lady art.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.17,0:50:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,喬治亞·歐姬芙不是個例外嗎{\fs14}\NWhat about Georgia O'Keeffe?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.17,0:50:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(198,33.283)}喬治亞·歐姬芙: 美國藝術家 20世紀的藝術大師之一
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.42,0:50:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼瑪格麗特 你從哪獲取靈感{\fs14}\NSo, Margaret, where did you get your ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.43,0:50:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,從我身邊的一切{\fs14}\NFrom the world around me ...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.29,0:50:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我鍾愛莫迪裡阿尼{\fs14}\N... and I just love Modigliani.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.29,0:50:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(200.4,34.948)}莫迪裡阿尼：意大利藝術家 畫家和雕塑家
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.29,0:50:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(236.4,59.919)}表現主義畫派的代表藝術家之一
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.82,0:50:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"莫迪"  誰啊{\fs14}\N"Monti" ... what?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.90,0:50:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 瑪格麗特{\fs14}\NFor Christ's sake, Margaret!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.58,0:50:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,迪克寫的是八卦專欄{\fs14}\NDick writes gossip column.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.75,0:50:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就講講家庭方面的內容{\fs14}\NStick to the family angle.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.58,0:50:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,給小簡兒也寫幾句吧{\fs14}\NGet a angle over little Janey over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.65,0:50:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,小有天賦哦{\fs14}\NWhat a talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.54,0:50:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧我們這一家子{\fs14}\NLook at these Keanes!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.27,0:50:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是切開我們的血管 流出來的都是顏料{\fs14}\NWhen you cut open our veins, we bleed oil!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.51,0:50:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 錦上添花{\fs14}\NAh, little treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.52,0:50:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我們基恩家的第四名畫家{\fs14}\NThe forth member of the painting Keane.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.67,0:50:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,莉莉寶貝 今天過得好嗎{\fs14}\NLily, sweetie, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.21,0:51:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸，我掉了顆牙，其他一切都好{\fs14}\NI'm fine dad, I lost a tooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.72,0:51:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,真的啊{\fs14}\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.51,0:51:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你和人打架了{\fs14}\NYou getting into a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.53,0:51:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有 它自己掉的{\fs14}\NNo, it fell out.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.72,0:51:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼需要我出面對付牙仙 {\fs14}\NWell, is the tooth fairy something I have to deal with?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.64,0:51:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是你媽已經解決了{\fs14}\Nor your mom alreay handled it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.23,0:51:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽已經解決了{\fs14}\NShe handled it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.89,0:51:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好 太好了{\fs14}\NGood, good, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.98,0:51:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,簡 過來帶 她參觀下你的房間{\fs14}\NJaney, come, show her the kids room.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.66,0:51:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,然後你們就自娛自樂吧{\fs14}\NAnd then you girls can join the fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.01,0:51:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 沃爾特 你從沒告訴我你還有個女兒{\fs14}\NHey, Walter, you never told me you had another daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.07,0:51:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒說嗎 可能吧{\fs14}\NDidn't I? sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.06,0:51:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,莉莉是我和前妻生的{\fs14}\NLily is from my first marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.83,0:51:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉失陪一下{\fs14}\NExcuse me, sorry, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.73,0:51:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,沃爾特 能和你說幾句嗎{\fs14}\NWalter, may I have a word with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.15,0:52:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 這到底是怎麼一回事 - 莉莉我女兒啊{\fs14}\N- What is going on in here? - That's Lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.60,0:52:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你提過吧{\fs14}\NI'm sure mentioned her.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.42,0:52:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有 你沒說過{\fs14}\NNo, you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.52,0:52:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她要搬來嗎 - 不會{\fs14}\N- Is she moving in? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.98,0:52:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,她媽這週末去拉斯維加斯了{\fs14}\NHer mother has gone to Vegas for the weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.02,0:52:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我本來應該每個月都帶她一次的{\fs14}\NI supposed to have her once a month ...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.71,0:52:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不過她媽不願意{\fs14}\N... but I don't make her mom ...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.03,0:52:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼可以隱瞞這麼大的事{\fs14}\NHow could you lie about something so big?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.33,0:52:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她是個乖女兒 - 我相信她是{\fs14}\N- Oh she is a very sweet girl. - I'm sure she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.65,0:52:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你女兒生活了這麼久 有抱怨過一句嗎{\fs14}\NWell I put up with your daughter, never said a peep.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.77,0:52:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我就當你沒說過這句話{\fs14}\NI'm gonna pretend you didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.48,0:52:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我道歉{\fs14}\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.89,0:52:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 把採訪做完再說吧{\fs14}\NPlease, let's just get through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.81,0:52:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,會指出沃爾特·基恩和保羅·高更有很多相似之處{\fs14}\N... Walter Keane and Paul Gauguin have a lot in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.81,0:52:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(190.8,30.786)}保羅·高更：法國後印象派畫家 雕塑家
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.01,0:52:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,兩人都放棄既成的事業去全球遊學{\fs14}\NBoth walk away from a career to travel the globe ...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.10,0:52:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我接觸過許多名流人士{\fs14}\NI've learn a lot of famous personalities. </ I>
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.81,0:52:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一小類人能適應鎂光燈下的生活{\fs14}\NOnly a certain type of creature can live in that spotlight. </ I>
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.13,0:52:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,沃爾特是得心應手{\fs14}\NWalter had a chops. </ I>
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.03,0:52:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪格麗特卻束手束腳{\fs14}\NMargaret not so much. </ I>
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.14,0:53:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 這是我畫的 - 真的嗎{\fs14}\N- I painted that. - really?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.77,0:53:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,很能喚起人的情感{\fs14}\NIt's very evocative.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.13,0:53:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,也很性感{\fs14}\Nsensual.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.62,0:53:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,MDH{\fs14}\NMDH
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.87,0:53:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你真神秘啊{\fs14}\NYou're so mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.71,0:53:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,恩 不用我的全名是因為人們{\fs14}\NYes, we don't use my name since people don't ...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.57,0:53:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不把女人的藝術品當回事{\fs14}\N... take women's art seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.41,0:53:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,MDH是我名字的首寫字母{\fs14}\NMDH is my initials.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.88,0:53:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多說幾句 我對命理學非常感興趣{\fs14}\NAnd more, I'm really interested in numerology,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.31,0:53:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道7是個幸運數字嗎{\fs14}\N you know 7 is a really good number.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.42,0:53:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,7{\fs14}\N7?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.92,0:53:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,湊巧的是 我的全名是瑪格麗特·多莉絲·霍金斯{\fs14}\NLuckily, my main name is Margaret Doris Hawkins
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.24,0:53:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"M" 是字母表裡的第13個字母 "D" 是第4個 "H" 第8個{\fs14}\N"M" is the 13 letter of the alphabet, "D" is 4, "H" 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.38,0:53:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以把13里的1和3相加{\fs14}\NAnd you add that up 1 and 3 in 13 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.56,0:53:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一場色彩的狂歡{\fs14}\Nan orgy of color!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.37,0:53:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,失陪一下{\fs14}\NExcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.29,0:54:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼就可以用4加上4 再加上8 得到16{\fs14}\NWhich makes 4 plus 4 plus 8 equal 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.89,0:54:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,然後1加6 得到7{\fs14}\NAnd 1 plus 6 equal 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.53,0:54:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪格麗特 借一步說話{\fs14}\NMagrate, one second?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.86,0:54:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 你都想些什麼東西啊 忘了遠景了{\fs14}\NGood God, what did you think about? longer vision?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.11,0:54:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你不說話天塌不下來{\fs14}\NCould you please help the world and shut your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.11,0:54:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你想讓他記住的唯一數字   就是標價{\fs14}\NThe only number you want in his head  ... is the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.45,0:54:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,一家兩口都是瘋子{\fs14}\NTwo nuts fell from the same tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.41,0:54:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,讓人難以忍受{\fs14}\NIt's insufferable.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.26,0:54:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,憑什麼他們賺的盆滿缽溢而我們卻毛都沒有{\fs14}\NWhy are we starving while they print money?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.08,0:54:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,因為他們的賣畫方法太天才了{\fs14}\NBecause that's how genius sells paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.91,0:54:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們不但賣畫作的印刷品 {\fs14}\NAnd they sell pictures of the paintings,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.83,0:54:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還賣印有印刷品圖案的明信片{\fs14}\N then they sell postcard of the pictures of the paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.34,0:54:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我打包票這畫我10分鐘就能整一幅{\fs14}\NI bet I could bang one out in 10 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.89,0:54:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,難道你不怕被人識破是贗品{\fs14}\NWouldn't you have to dealt with the sincerity.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.94,0:54:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,消費者哪會分的出來{\fs14}\NWell the costumer wouldn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.66,0:54:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,老天  蔚然成風了{\fs14}\NChrist ... it's a movement.
