Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.25,0:54:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,藝術界新貴 基恩
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.49,0:55:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,伍德賽德 加州 1963年
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.96,0:55:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,老天 我還以為走錯門了{\fs14}\NMy God! I thought I had the wrong address.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.07,0:55:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我這路途是比較遠{\fs14}\NI know it's a really long drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.57,0:55:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,實話說我都不敢相信住在這裡{\fs14}\NHonestly I can't believe I live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.67,0:55:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白{\fs14}\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.82,0:55:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你這房子得有2英畝吧 - 一個游泳池 5間臥室{\fs14}\N- You got two acres. - A pool, Five bedrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.97,0:55:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我認為有點大得離譜{\fs14}\NI thought it was excessive.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.10,0:55:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,因為就我們3個人住在這{\fs14}\NSince there is only three of us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.01,0:55:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,都有好久沒見你了{\fs14}\NBeen so long since I see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.65,0:55:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊{\fs14}\NI know
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.61,0:55:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這距北灘30英里 感覺上好像有300英里{\fs14}\NNorth beach is 30 miles, might as well be 300.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.53,0:55:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是整天忙於應酬那些新交的富人朋友啊{\fs14}\NWell, you probably busy hanging out with all your new rich buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.90,0:55:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,饒了我吧 那些是沃爾特的朋友{\fs14}\NPlease! those are Walter's friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.21,0:55:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他經常帶人來{\fs14}\NHe brings people by.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.89,0:55:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,「 海灘男孩 」來過這{\fs14}\NThe Beach Boys came by.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.89,0:55:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(189,30.786)}海灘男孩: 一搖滾樂隊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.67,0:56:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你餓不餓{\fs14}\NAre you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.73,0:56:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有點渴{\fs14}\NI'm thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.45,0:56:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,剛搬來時 我覺得這個小吧檯有點奢侈多餘了{\fs14}\NWhen I moved in, I thought a wet bar is kind extravagant.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.94,0:56:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不過你會驚訝它有多好使{\fs14}\NBut you would be surprise how much issues can get out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.55,0:56:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那談談沃爾特吧{\fs14}\NSo how is Walter?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.92,0:56:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他再開心不過了{\fs14}\NHe couldn't be happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.97,0:56:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他夢想要的全都有了{\fs14}\NHe has everything he's ever dreamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.05,0:56:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你也一樣 真讓人羨慕{\fs14}\NSo do you, fabulous!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.16,0:56:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊是你的畫室{\fs14}\NIs that your arts studio?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.94,0:56:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你可不想去那 - 我想瞅一眼{\fs14}\N- You don't want to go in there. - I wanna take a peek.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.48,0:56:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我想看看巨成功的藝術家是如何工作的{\fs14}\NI want to see what work phase of wildly successful artist looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.40,0:56:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,別 別去{\fs14}\NNo no no...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.56,0:56:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,荻安 請別下去好嗎{\fs14}\NDeeAnn, Please do not go down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.88,0:56:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你不可以進去{\fs14}\NYou can't go in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.96,0:56:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,這也是沃爾特的畫室{\fs14}\NWalter paints here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.76,0:56:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,沃爾特現在在家嗎{\fs14}\NIs Walter home now?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.86,0:56:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這是搞什麼啊{\fs14}\NWhat the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.15,0:57:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼{\fs14}\NNothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.48,0:57:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是請荻安過來看看{\fs14}\NI just invite DeeAnn over.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.94,0:57:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我不喜歡讓人看到沒完工的畫作{\fs14}\NYou know I don't like anyone seeing my work before it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.75,0:57:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你和你的作品都是騙人的垃圾{\fs14}\NYou and your all none representation crap are fraud!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.56,0:57:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,閉上你的臭嘴 沃爾特{\fs14}\NShut up, you're so full of shit! Walter.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.54,0:57:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,滾出我的宅子{\fs14}\NGet out of my house ...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.72,0:57:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,滾出我的豪宅{\fs14}\N... get out of my big house!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.74,0:57:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,滾去碼頭向漁夫{\fs14}\NGo back selling your sculpture ...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.86,0:57:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,兜售你的垃圾吧{\fs14}\N... in fishmen's wharf!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.22,0:57:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你去死{\fs14}\NFuck you!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.36,0:57:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我再也不想看到她來{\fs14}\NI don't want her ever invited here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.16,0:57:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會了{\fs14}\NI won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.22,0:58:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好了 簡 我得開工了 - 我可以跟著去嗎{\fs14}\N- All right Jane, I'm get to work. - Can I come?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.90,0:58:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 我永遠都不能去{\fs14}\NNo, I can't ever come.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.05,0:58:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,其實我根本就不該問的{\fs14}\NNo, I shouldn't even ask.
