Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.13,0:58:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒聽過嗎 這裡謝絕訪客{\fs14}\NDidn't you hear that there is no visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.82,0:58:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,命運還真是作弄人啊{\fs14}\NThis is what it comes to, huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.93,0:58:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你現在是我唯一可以傾述秘密的生物{\fs14}\NYou're the only living soul I can tell my secret to.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.65,0:58:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那我坦白 它們都是我畫的{\fs14}\NWell, I painted them.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.76,0:58:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,它們一個個   都是我畫的{\fs14}\NI did ... every single one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.97,0:58:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,每一幅 " 大眼睛 "{\fs14}\NEvery "Big Eyes".
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.52,0:58:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我畫的{\fs14}\NMe.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.27,0:58:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,可是除了你沒人會知道{\fs14}\NBut no one will ever know but you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.90,0:59:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在又要動手再畫一幅{\fs14}\NI'm gonna paint another one right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.28,0:59:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,要是沃爾特在這的話肯定會說{\fs14}\NTake Walter off ...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.89,0:59:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我打算畫一個對著狗狗自言自語的小瘋婆子了{\fs14}\N... I'll paint one about a crazy girl talking to a dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.32,1:00:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,今天收穫不小{\fs14}\NProductive day today.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.82,1:00:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,碰上新鮮出爐的傳聞{\fs14}\NStumble on some hot gossip.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.42,1:00:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,從台北直飛的蔣介石夫人{\fs14}\NMadame Chiang Kai-shek is coming to town ...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.77,1:00:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,要來我們這裡{\fs14}\N... straight from Taipei.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.30,1:00:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我們得贈送幅畫給她 {\fs14}\NI think we should present her with a painting,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.64,1:00:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找迪克來報道{\fs14}\Nget Dick to flack it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.39,1:00:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 找迪克幹嘛 我新結識了一個合眾國際社的夥計{\fs14}\NWell, hell with Dick, I met a new guy at UPI
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.98,1:00:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,她沒準喜歡你畫的某一幅街景呢{\fs14}\NMaybe she'll like one of your street scenes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.43,1:00:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎 我拿不準{\fs14}\NYeah, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.11,1:00:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得你可以描個唐人街的背景{\fs14}\NI thought you could rip off a doodler of china town
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.81,1:00:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加上個可愛的小女孩{\fs14}\Nwith a cute little girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.99,1:00:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,大眼睛稍微畫彎點就成{\fs14}\NSort of big eye slanting eye thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.64,1:00:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不行{\fs14}\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.85,1:01:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,她可是個政要{\fs14}\NShe is a dignitary.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.55,1:01:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你的親筆大作才配的上她{\fs14}\NShe deserve a piece come straight from you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.18,1:01:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你真這麼認為{\fs14}\NYou think?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.44,1:01:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能對{\fs14}\NMaybe you're right.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.33,1:01:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,她的宮殿裡也許就缺少一幅巴黎的街景畫{\fs14}\NShe probably doesn't has a Parisian street scene hanging in her palace.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.53,1:01:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,除非蔣介石夫人恰好已經有了一幅申景華的作品{\fs14}\NUnless Madame Chiang Kai-shek already has a S. Cenic.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.37,1:01:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 申景華是誰 - 那位畫家啊{\fs14}\N- What's that? - A S.Cenic.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.59,1:01:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那位畫了你之前所有作品的畫家{\fs14}\NThat's the painter that painted all your early work.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.48,1:01:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你說的實景畫吧{\fs14}\NIt's scenic.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.19,1:01:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我在巴黎時的綽號{\fs14}\NThat's my nickname in Paris.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.14,1:01:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我在美院的同學都很喜歡我畫的實景畫{\fs14}\NAll my art school pals love my scenic view so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.24,1:01:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他們見到我就會提實景畫 當然由於他們發音不準 ...{\fs14}\NThey call me, well they couldn't pronouce properly ...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.57,1:01:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,叫著叫著就成了申景華{\fs14}\N... so they call me S. Cenic.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.44,1:01:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你越是撒謊 就越顯得渺小{\fs14}\NThe more you lie, the smaller you seem.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.66,1:01:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼可以指責我撒謊{\fs14}\NHow dare you accused me of lying?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.89,1:01:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我對我早期畫的實景畫相當自豪{\fs14}\NI'm proud of my early scenics.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.95,1:01:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那你為什麼只把名字畫掉{\fs14}\NThen why did you painted over the name?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.08,1:01:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,給你個忠告{\fs14}\NPiece of advice ...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.00,1:02:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,水溶性的顏料塗在哪都是廢的{\fs14}\N... never use water base over nowhere ...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.63,1:02:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我一刮就掉了{\fs14}\N... I'm just flay right off.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.82,1:02:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你盡說什麼瘋話啊{\fs14}\NYou sound like crazy for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.64,1:02:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你見過我畫畫{\fs14}\NYou see me paint.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.47,1:02:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有 我沒見過{\fs14}\NNo, I haven't
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.17,1:02:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直以為 我見過{\fs14}\NI always thought ... I had ...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.79,1:02:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不過就像海市蜃樓{\fs14}\N... but it's like a mirage.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.35,1:02:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我從遠處看 你像個畫家{\fs14}\NI'm in distance, you look like a painter.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.31,1:02:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,等一走近 煙消雲散無影蹤{\fs14}\NUp close, there is not much there.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.92,1:02:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我去過巴黎{\fs14}\NI've been to Paris!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.64,1:02:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我在法蘭西藝術院上的學{\fs14}\NI studied at the Beaux Arts!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.31,1:02:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,還上過大茅屋學院{\fs14}\NAt grande Chaumiere!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.87,1:02:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我在盧浮宮無數次的觀摩各種大師的偉大作品{\fs14}\NI spent hours and hours at the Louvre staring at the great of the masters!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.29,1:02:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本就沒去過巴黎吧{\fs14}\NHave you even been to Paris?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.57,1:03:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我是想 我太想成為藝術家了可總是事與願違{\fs14}\NI wanted it, I so wanted to become a artist, just never turn out so well.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.33,1:03:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我請你以後都別在來這裡睡覺了{\fs14}\NI don't want you sleep here any longer.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.83,1:03:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,還有三間空出來的臥室任你挑呢{\fs14}\NThere are three extra bedroom in this house, go pick one.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.57,1:03:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 後面還有多少貨 - 我不清楚 可能3000張吧{\fs14}\N- How many more this under back? - I don't know, maybe 3000?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.78,1:03:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那個印刷廠 - 女士 我想問下{\fs14}\N- Does the printer ... - Excuse me, Mrs.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.99,1:03:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 這幅畫的價格 - 快去，我請你是幹嘛的？{\fs14}\N- How much this painting? - Go! what do I pay you for?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.90,1:04:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,又是她的 我的畫一幅都沒人要{\fs14}\NNot even one of mine, one of hers.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.59,1:04:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,1964年紐約世博會{\fs14}\N1964 New York World's Fair Construction Races Toward April Opening
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.49,1:04:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這可改變不了什麼{\fs14}\NThis doesn't change anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.25,1:04:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我知道了你的真面目 - 噢，誰在乎啊{\fs14}\N- I know the truth. - Oh who cares?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.95,1:04:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許是時候進行些調整了{\fs14}\NMaybe it's time to shake things off,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.83,1:04:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該把MDH的畫都簽成我的名字{\fs14}\Nstart putting my name under the MDHs.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.57,1:04:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不行{\fs14}\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.25,1:04:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,別做夢了 把" 孤兒" 給你已經讓我悔恨萬分{\fs14}\NAbsolutely not, I already hate myself giving you the waifs.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.41,1:04:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,小聲點{\fs14}\NQuiet!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.75,1:04:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 別講那麼大聲 - 從今往後我講多大聲你管不著{\fs14}\N- Don't raise your voice. - I will talk as loud as I want.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.10,1:04:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你想都別想 不然就要你好看{\fs14}\NNo, you won't, or I have you whacked.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.86,1:04:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼{\fs14}\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.54,1:04:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你敢告訴任何人 我就找人收拾了你{\fs14}\NIf you tell anyone, I'll have you taking £?...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.85,1:04:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我人脈廣 還記得班度奇的侄子嗎 那個賣酒的{\fs14}\NI know people, remember Banducci's cousin? liquor wholesaler.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.33,1:04:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你這是威脅我{\fs14}\NAre you threatening me?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.96,1:04:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 殺了我{\fs14}\NFine, kill me.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.99,1:05:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 我守口如瓶這麼多年 從未有一次{\fs14}\NMy God, I keep our secret for years, never once ...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.25,1:05:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你能體會我有多不容易嗎{\fs14}\NYou know how hard this is been for me?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.06,1:05:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有一個朋友{\fs14}\NI don't have any friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.93,1:05:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,對自己的孩子撒謊{\fs14}\NI lie to my own child.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.94,1:05:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是人生如藝啊 哈 一個流淚的基恩{\fs14}\NLife imitating art, a crying Keane.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.20,1:05:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,沃爾特 你到底想要什麼{\fs14}\NWalter, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.21,1:05:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都在你的算計之中{\fs14}\NEverything was your calculated.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.47,1:05:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我們又回到初次約會的地點{\fs14}\NWe're back where we have our first date.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.19,1:05:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我不否認我需要你 你才是有天賦的那個人{\fs14}\NI don't deny I need you, you're the one with the gift.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.39,1:05:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,現在有一個大好機會{\fs14}\NNow there is a shot ...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.47,1:05:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我興奮都發抖了{\fs14}\NI'm shaking, I'm so exciting!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.71,1:05:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,紐約世博會{\fs14}\NThe New York World's Fair.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.56,1:05:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,預計七千萬遊客{\fs14}\N70 millions visitors.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.64,1:05:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,開園那天我將揭示我的宏偉大作{\fs14}\NOpening day I unveil my master piece.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.83,1:05:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什麼宏偉大作 - 問得太對了{\fs14}\N- What master piece? - Exact.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.36,1:06:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我們一直以來聽得最多的是什麼{\fs14}\NWhat have we been listening all this time?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.55,1:06:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,達芬奇有他的 " 蒙娜麗莎 " 雷諾阿的 " 船上的午宴 "{\fs14}\NDa Vinci has his Mona Lisa, Renoir has his Boatmen's lunch.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.42,1:06:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我的留名大作在哪{\fs14}\NWhere is my defining statement?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.85,1:06:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你有點瘋了吧{\fs14}\NYou sound insane.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.04,1:06:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,藝術家怎麼可以自以為是欽定自己的名作{\fs14}\NArtist doesn't just annouce his master piece.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.31,1:06:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼不行{\fs14}\NWhy not?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.56,1:06:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當米開朗基羅揮汗如雨的繪製《創世紀》時 {\fs14}\NDid Michelangelo know he is hitting a home run
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.13,1:06:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他知道自己留下的是傳世神作嗎{\fs14}\Nwhen he's on his back painting Sistine Chapel?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.37,1:06:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那可花了他整整四年{\fs14}\NThat take him four years.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.73,1:06:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,最好的部分我還沒說呢{\fs14}\NBut there is the best part.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.95,1:06:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這是給聯合國兒童基金會的{\fs14}\NIt's for Unicef!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.41,1:06:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,聯合國兒童基金會贊助的教育館{\fs14}\NUnicef sponsors the hall of education.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.02,1:06:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我們終於可以給全世界孩子做點貢獻了{\fs14}\NWe can finally give back to the children of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.95,1:06:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,羅威爾·托馬斯 世博會專題報道{\fs14}\NWORLD'S FAIR REPORT WITH LOWELL THOMAS
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.67,1:06:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,大家好 </ I>{\fs14}\NHello, everybody. </ I>
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.30,1:06:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我是羅威爾·托馬斯 </ I>{\fs14}\NI'm Lowell Thomas. </ I>
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.96,1:06:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,在我身後就是即將成為{\fs14}\NStanding in front one of what will soon be ... </ I>
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.37,1:06:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,現代世界的奇觀之一 </ I>{\fs14}\N... one of the wonders of the modern world. </ I>
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.99,1:07:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,當有人問我為什麼她選擇留下{\fs14}\NWhen people asked me why did she stay. </ I>
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.29,1:07:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是膽怯 還是沒信心{\fs14}\NWas it fear, lack of confidence? </ i>
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.89,1:07:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪格麗特是被困在了自己添磚加瓦造成的謊言裡 {\fs14}\NMargaret was trapped in the lie that she helped creat. </ I>
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.08,1:07:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,試圖掩蓋只會徒增罪孽罷了{\fs14}\NAnother cover up is worth than a crime. </ I>
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.72,1:07:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼你要跟他們允諾這麼大尺幅的畫作{\fs14}\NWhy did you have to promise them similar the size?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.45,1:07:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,因為它可以裝下所有種族 膚色的孩子{\fs14}\NBecause it has encompass all children, all races.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.88,1:07:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,成百上千受難的面孔走向無盡之地{\fs14}\NHundreds of stricken faces marching to infinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.38,1:07:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,沃爾特·基恩的巔峰之作{\fs14}\NThe ultimate of the Walter Keane.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.97,1:07:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一個廣告公關告訴我現在是時候推出一本茶几讀物了{\fs14}\NA publicist says it's good timing to put out a coffee table book.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.92,1:07:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那種 "時尚"  "明日大師" 之類的{\fs14}\NYou know, ?oClassy??, ?oTomorrow's  Masters??.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.93,1:07:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他們需要一些我的早期畫冊 風格成型史什麼的{\fs14}\NThey need my early portfolio, artistic evolution.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.99,1:07:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,對啊 你那些早期草圖都在哪呢{\fs14}\NYes, where are all of your preliminary sketches?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.58,1:07:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你讀美院大把的時間 應該{\fs14}\NAll that time you spent in art school seem to ...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.81,1:07:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,積累下一疊疊早期的練習畫冊 {\fs14}\N... well laid all of your useful experiment,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.75,1:07:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各種碳筆草圖什麼的{\fs14}\Nall these unfinished charcoals.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.67,1:07:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,可能就在這附近吧 你找找{\fs14}\NCould be around here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.17,1:08:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你只是說笑而與 我說的都是些好點子{\fs14}\NI know you been sarcastic, these are good idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.34,1:08:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,多加些孤兒進去 還有早期的自畫像{\fs14}\NPut in more orphans, early self portraits.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.53,1:08:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,請出去吧 別打擾我工作{\fs14}\NGet out here, I'm try to work.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.64,1:08:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,媽 晚飯吃什麼啊{\fs14}\NMom, what about dinner?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.69,1:08:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,媽 你在家嗎{\fs14}\NMom, are you home?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.88,1:09:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,簡 這是沃爾特的畫室 你快出去{\fs14}\NJane, this is Walter's studio, you need to leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.86,1:09:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,媽 我知道{\fs14}\NMom, I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.01,1:09:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不 你啥都不知道{\fs14}\NNo, you don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.17,1:09:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我不再是小孩子了{\fs14}\NI'm not a child anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.95,1:09:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,五 六頁 我有漏了什麼嗎{\fs14}\NFive... six pages. Is something here I missing?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.36,1:09:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他就像呼啦圈 怎麼都甩不掉{\fs14}\NHe's like the hula hoop, he just won't go away!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.34,1:10:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,"  將會在教育館的大廳揭幕 "{\fs14}\N" ... will be unveil in the grand pavilion of the hall of education ... "
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.88,1:10:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,," 享譽世界的藝術家被選作 "{\fs14}\N" ... internationally celebrated artists been selected ... "
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.05,1:10:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,," 將代表全世界兒童的渴望 "{\fs14}\N" ... will represent the aspiration of the children worldwide. "
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.50,1:10:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,荒謬{\fs14}\NThis is absurd!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.24,1:10:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,選舉委員會都有哪些人{\fs14}\NUnder who was on selection committee?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.78,1:10:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 之前並不存在一個委員會{\fs14}\NOh, there wasn't a committee precede.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.36,1:10:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,只是我 艾德 傑羅姆和她的妻子辦了個午宴而已{\fs14}\NWe just had luncheon, with me, Ed, and Jerome, Jerome's wife ...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.54,1:10:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不過按章程我們不能邀請候選人{\fs14}\NThough technically we didn't invite submissions.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.31,1:10:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,基恩先生就直接給我們打了個電話{\fs14}\NMr. Keane just contact us directly.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.97,1:10:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,紐約市 1964年四月{\fs14}\NNew York City, April. 1964
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.77,1:10:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,高興點嘛{\fs14}\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.98,1:10:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,週三世博會開幕 週四我們的書開售{\fs14}\NWednesday the World's Fair opens, Thursday our books on sell.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.42,1:10:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,週五我就申請離婚{\fs14}\NFriday I file for divorce.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.59,1:11:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼你總要這麼掃興{\fs14}\NWhy are you always so miserable?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.36,1:11:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我可要好好享受這個下午{\fs14}\NWell, I'm going to enjoy my afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.55,1:11:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂斯代爾女士 鄙人沃爾特·基恩{\fs14}\NMrs. Tisdale, Walter Keane.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.26,1:11:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想感謝你辦的這個萬分迷人的晚會{\fs14}\NI just want to thank you  for hosting this absolutely enchanting soiree.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.16,1:11:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你太客氣了{\fs14}\NYou're most welcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.02,1:11:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,基恩 你看了紐約時報嗎{\fs14}\NKeane, did you see the Times?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.28,1:11:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有功夫看{\fs14}\NHonestly,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.09,1:11:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一整天都在為這個重要場合忙上忙下的{\fs14}\NI've been so busy all day preparing for this lovely occasion.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.71,1:11:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我建議你還是去看一下{\fs14}\NI think you should read the Times.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.32,1:11:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,世博會大廳主題畫作選定基恩的作品{\fs14}\NArt: World's Fair Pavilion Selects Theme Painting
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.30,1:12:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,低劣 怪誕 畫者毫無品味{\fs14}\NAppalling, grotesque, tasteless hack.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.34,1:12:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼有人能說出這麼傷人的話{\fs14}\NHow can somebody say something so cruel?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.08,1:12:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,傷的是我的名譽 你幹嘛要在乎{\fs14}\NWhy do you care? this my name being drag through mud.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.73,1:12:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他也在這{\fs14}\NIs he here?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.60,1:12:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,在 或許大家最好都{\fs14}\NYes, which is perhaps why it's best for everybody if ...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.33,1:12:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,誰寫的這篇狗屁文章{\fs14}\NWho wrote this shit?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.87,1:12:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,基恩先生 這不是會議室{\fs14}\NMr. Keane, this is not the venue.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.85,1:12:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,或許你想給編輯寫封信更合適吧{\fs14}\NPerhaps you would like to write a letter to the editor?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.80,1:12:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你在怕什麼{\fs14}\NWhat are you afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.72,1:12:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因為大眾喜歡我的作品{\fs14}\NJust because people like my work,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.62,1:12:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以必然意味著水準低{\fs14}\Nthat means automatically it's bad?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.84,1:12:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不一定 不過它也稱不上是藝術{\fs14}\NNo, but it doesn't make art either.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.73,1:12:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,藝術應該是昇華 而不是一味迎合{\fs14}\NArt should elevate, not pander.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.56,1:12:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,特別是掛在教育館的作品{\fs14}\NParticularly at the Hall of Education.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.48,1:12:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂個屁{\fs14}\NYou have no idea!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.02,1:12:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼有人要去幹評論 因為他不會動手只會動口{\fs14}\NWhy does someone become a critic? because he can not creat.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.02,1:12:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 你只會說這種陳詞濫調嗎{\fs14}\NOh dear, that mouldy chastener.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.60,1:12:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,閉上你的狗嘴{\fs14}\NDon't interrupt!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.62,1:12:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本不能體會我傾注了多少情感進去{\fs14}\NYou don't know what's like to put your emotion out there,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.76,1:12:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像赤身裸體的面對世人{\fs14}\Nnaked for the whole world to see!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.41,1:13:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,哪來的情感 這水準就是爛大街的印刷品{\fs14}\NWhat emotions? it's synthetic hack work.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.15,1:13:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你的「大作」有無數的基恩{\fs14}\NYour "master piece" has infinite Keanes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.84,1:13:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就代表低俗得無下限{\fs14}\NWhich makes it infinite kitsch.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.16,1:13:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,最低俗的人又怎麼樣{\fs14}\NWhat is wrong with the Lowest common denominator?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.78,1:14:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這個國家不是靠這些人會有今天{\fs14}\NThat's what this country was build of!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.23,1:14:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把他們都告了{\fs14}\NI'm gonna sue everybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.74,1:14:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,要告他們每一個人{\fs14}\NI'm gonna sue everybody!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.84,1:14:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我要告那個娘炮評論家 告世博會{\fs14}\NI want to sue this pansy critic, sue the World's Fair.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.17,1:14:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要扳倒聯合國兒童基金會 {\fs14}\NI'm gonna take down Unicef,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.09,1:14:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斷了他們的財路{\fs14}\Nor his precous little box of dime.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.22,1:14:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不過我告不了你吧 是不是{\fs14}\NBut I can't sue you, can I?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.17,1:15:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是最終黑手吧 {\fs14}\NYou're really ultimate betrayal,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.18,1:15:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用那幅畫來整倒我{\fs14}\N you fail me with that painting.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.59,1:15:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你從多愁善感墮落成俗不可耐{\fs14}\NYou cross over from sentimentality to kitsch.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.42,1:15:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,沃爾特 住手{\fs14}\NWalter, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.35,1:15:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你就想讓我當眾出醜 你就想看我被人笑話{\fs14}\NYou like making me look bad, you enjoy people laughing at me?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.46,1:15:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,開門 快開門 讓我進去{\fs14}\NOpen it up, open it up! let me in!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.63,1:16:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我看得到你{\fs14}\NI can see you!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.69,1:16:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我要燒死你{\fs14}\NI'm gonna burn you out!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.34,1:16:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你嘗嘗原子彈爆炸的威力{\fs14}\NYou gonna blow up like atomic bomb!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.89,1:16:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你躲哪了{\fs14}\NWhere are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.62,1:16:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我對不起你 我不是個合格的母親{\fs14}\NI am so sorry, I was not the mother I could've been.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.20,1:17:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,多年前我就該這麼做的{\fs14}\NI should've done this years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.33,1:17:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我們真的要走嗎 連衣服都沒帶{\fs14}\NCan't believe we're going, We don't have any clothes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.08,1:17:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要去的地方 不需多少衣服{\fs14}\NWhere we're going, we don't need much!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.93,1:17:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,夏威夷{\fs14}\NHawaii.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.84,1:17:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎{\fs14}\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.20,1:17:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,恩 去夏威夷 因為那裡是天堂{\fs14}\NYes, Hawaii, because it's paradise there.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.13,1:17:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你會見識那的鳥語花香 風景秀麗{\fs14}\NYou know there're birds, flowers, beautiful colours.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.78,1:17:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我們會開啟一段新的人生{\fs14}\NWe gonna make a new life for ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.16,1:17:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我的乖女兒{\fs14}\NThat's my girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.93,1:17:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,火奴魯魯 一年後{\fs14}\NHonolulu, One year later.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.60,1:18:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你躲得真夠遠的啊 我還以為再也見不到你了{\fs14}\NYou're sure hard to track down, I thought I may never find you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.03,1:18:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,沃爾特{\fs14}\NWalter ...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.93,1:18:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我有點煩躁{\fs14}\NI was a little agitated.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.65,1:18:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我收到一封從未見過的信{\fs14}\NI got this strangest paper in the mail today.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.07,1:18:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是法定分居協議書 {\fs14}\NIt's a decreed legal seperation,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.92,1:18:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會很感激你把它簽了{\fs14}\NI would appreciated it if you sign it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.05,1:18:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你難道不覺得這事急了點嗎{\fs14}\NAren't you acting a little rush?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.18,1:18:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,沃爾特 我想要離婚{\fs14}\NWalter, I want a divorce.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.78,1:18:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說的話讓人難過 {\fs14}\NHurts to hear you say these words,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.43,1:18:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到我們也會有這一天{\fs14}\Nthat's sure how we come to this.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.48,1:19:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你想分居多久我都可以答應 只要{\fs14}\NI suppose I could agree just split as long as...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.22,1:19:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你今後作的每一幅畫都簽我的名字{\fs14}\N... as you sign me all rest of every painting you ever produce.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.57,1:19:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那成交{\fs14}\NIf that's the price.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.39,1:19:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的同意{\fs14}\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.50,1:19:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好 那麼我們還得商討下將來的收入問題{\fs14}\NOk, well, then we have to consider future revenue strings ...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.98,1:19:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,老天 沃爾特 你要賺多少錢才滿意{\fs14}\NMy God, Walter! how much more money do you need?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.31,1:19:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想擺脫我 就仔細聽好了{\fs14}\NIf you want me out of your life, here is my bargain.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.13,1:19:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你得給我畫上百張孤兒{\fs14}\NYou have to paint me a hundred more waifs ...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.35,1:19:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,上百張簽有沃爾特·基恩的畫{\fs14}\N... a hundred more Walter Keanes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.90,1:19:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,簡 我要去趟郵局 想跟我一起嗎{\fs14}\NJane, I'm gonna go to post stop, you wanna come?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.29,1:19:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不了 我想去衝浪{\fs14}\NNo, I'm gonna go surf's game.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.74,1:19:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡 我覺得你的朋友都有點野 {\fs14}\NJane, I think your friends are a little wild.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.54,1:19:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰不是啊 老媽{\fs14}\NWho's not, mom?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.54,1:19:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你有點不可理喻{\fs14}\NYou're impossible.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.00,1:19:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我們大老遠的搬到{\fs14}\NYou move all the way ...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.93,1:19:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏威夷來 我這才交上幾個朋友 {\fs14}\N... to Hawaii, and I actually make some friends,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.10,1:19:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可你動不動就發他們的牢騷{\fs14}\Nall you do is complain about them.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.04,1:19:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,也許你得交幾個朋友了{\fs14}\NMaybe you need to make some.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.66,1:20:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我不可以讓人來家裡的{\fs14}\NYou know that I can not have people over to the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.07,1:20:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那倒是 不然他們會看到你的寶貝畫作{\fs14}\NThat's right, or else they would see the precious paintings.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.73,1:20:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 我們在這附近挨家挨戶的傳遞一條重要信息{\fs14}\NHello, we visit everyone in this neighbourhood with an important message.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.60,1:20:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我們想跟你分享一些{\fs14}\NWe have something to share with you ..
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.10,1:20:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,關於上帝的王國會給人類{\fs14}\N... about the wonderful things the God's kindom  ...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.60,1:20:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,帶來的福祉{\fs14}\N... would do for mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.51,1:20:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那在我待的地方 我沒看到多少好事{\fs14}\NWell from where I'm standing, I don't see much good anywhere ...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.01,1:21:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,儘是些斯文敗類互相算計對方{\fs14}\N... just a lot of pride deviant people treating each other poorly.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.87,1:21:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道提摩太后書3章1至5節嗎{\fs14}\NDo you know what it says in Timothy 3: 1-5?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.32,1:21:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,末世必有危險的日子來到{\fs14}\NIn the last days, critical time hard to dealt with will be here ...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.97,1:21:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,因為那時人要專顧自己{\fs14}\N... for men would be lovers of themselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.31,1:21:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,聽起來像我前夫{\fs14}\NSounds like my ex-husband.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.31,1:21:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你想請我們進去嗎{\fs14}\NWould you like to come in?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.10,1:21:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡說了「耶和華的信徒必須事事誠實」{\fs14}\NIt says right here, "a worshiper of Jehovah must be honest in all things".
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.45,1:21:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是不敢相信你讓人進我們家了{\fs14}\NI just can't believe you let people in the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.65,1:21:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這還說了「謊言替代不了真相 願竊賊改邪歸正」{\fs14}\NIt also says, "No lies speak the truth, let stealer steal no more."
